{"tid":2921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你估你老婆係港女 結局會唔會一樣","createTime":"2016-11-26T03:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T03:50:05.000Z","uid":17003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c87acfa50b9ec8179f8ef7c24390c96d5d36dd3c","tid":2921,"uid":17003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"(港版阿信的故事) 老婆孭住個女返工出意外 沉迷打機老公終用心工作<br />\n<br />\n上水拉麵店「麵家山下」，店主是個八十後，終日沉迷打機，無所事事。因娶了一個日本女孩，還有了孩子。為了孩子，日本妻子鼓勵他開拉麵店，還力到人到幫他一齊打理，感動了他，令他努力工作，承擔家庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/114720_5e9a5115f202047a3cbbd40d0caa0c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F114720_5e9a5115f202047a3cbbd40d0caa0c26.jpg&h=fc4ff553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://etw.nextmedia.com/etw/videoWallDetail.html?id=10064&amp;filter=1&amp;ga=20161120%2F%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93%2F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E9%98%BF%E4%BF%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%8B%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E5%AD%AD%E4%BD%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E5%87%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96+%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%B5%82%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextmedia.com%2Fetw%2FvideoWallDetail.html%3Fid%3D10064%26filter%3D1%26ga%3D20161120%252F%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593%252F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%252F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E9%2598%25BF%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25AD%25AD%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596%2B%25E6%25B2%2589%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259